    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Super Ultimate Party Game</strong> 是一款向经典派对游戏致敬的作品。使用独特的道具，参与原创的迷你游戏，收集最多的宝藏，躲避搞怪的障碍，击败你的朋友！支持 1-4 名玩家本地或在线游玩，也可以与 AI 机器人一起畅玩！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>搞怪游戏事件</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >各种障碍挡在你通往胜利的道路上！躲开它们，或者利用它们来捣乱你的朋友！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290950/extras/d5194d404ea34c51ca8c66a3c98fd7aa.poster.avif?t=1751756590\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290950/extras/d5194d404ea34c51ca8c66a3c98fd7aa.webm?t=1751756590\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290950/extras/d5194d404ea34c51ca8c66a3c98fd7aa.mp4?t=1751756590\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>动作满满的迷你游戏</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在主游戏回合之间挑战迷你游戏，或者进入专属的迷你游戏模式畅玩！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290950/extras/8eae2ad7f847b5c43793f3cff6428be4.poster.avif?t=1751756590\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290950/extras/8eae2ad7f847b5c43793f3cff6428be4.webm?t=1751756590\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290950/extras/8eae2ad7f847b5c43793f3cff6428be4.mp4?t=1751756590\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>奇趣道具</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用独特的奇趣道具助你一步步接近目标——或者阻止你的朋友达成他们的目标！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290950/extras/8ab507eb5255533a17e598040d391c7d.poster.avif?t=1751756590\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290950/extras/8ab507eb5255533a17e598040d391c7d.webm?t=1751756590\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290950/extras/8ab507eb5255533a17e598040d391c7d.mp4?t=1751756590\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
